snippet.title: Malaysia Flight 370 possibly at an Abandoned Airport in Vietnam?

localized.description:
A look at the recent facts surrounding the disappearance of Malaysia Flight 370. Is it possible it was diverted to a airport in Vietnam that's not in use?

Sources: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_airports_in_Vietnam
http://foxnews.com
http://theguardian.com
